HEADWORD: mad-dog weed
<hw>mad-dog weed</hw></mhw>
<pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>An American mint (<spn>Scutellaria
lateriflora</spn>) that yields a resinous exudate used esp. formerly as
an antispasmodic.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> blue pimpernel, blue skullcap, <spn>Scutellaria
lateriflora</spn>.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

